workouts.title: Workout
workouts.introText:
You've built a base of upper-body strength, now let's push for more. This workout will get your pecs and triceps firing to deliver an epic burn.


Get your form locked down with the exercise tutorial before adding weight.


If you want to cool down after working out, you'll find the link to stretching sessions at the top of each week of workouts.

groups.summary: Find your intensity and get your muscles ready to work.
